{"results":[{"aya":"043","id":4718,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"在赛莫德人的故事里，也有一种迹象。当时，有人对他们说：你们暂时享受吧！","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"044","id":4719,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"他们曾违抗他们主的命令，故疾雷毁灭了他们，同时，他们眼见刑罚降临，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"045","id":4720,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"他们未能站起，他们也未能自卫。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"046","id":4721,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"以前，我毁灭了努哈的宗族，他们确是悖逆的民众。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"047","id":4722,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"天，我曾以权力建造它，我确是大能的；","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"048","id":4723,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"地，我曾铺张它。美哉铺张者！","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"049","id":4724,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"我将每种物造成配偶，以便你们觉悟。","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":9,"previousPage":"/zh/s051-6.json","nextPage":"/zh/s051-8.json"}}